data.title: J-E-S-U-S Cheer Song

data.text:
Lyrics:

Leader: Give me a “J”.

Group: “J” you’ve got your “J”. You’ve got your “J”.

Leader: Now give me an “E”.

Group: “E” you’ve got your “E”. You’ve got your “E”.

Leader: Now give me an “S”.

Group: “S” you’ve got your “S”. You’ve got your “S”.

Leader: Give me a “U”.

Group: “U” you’ve got your “U”. You’ve got your “U”.

Leader: Now give me an “S”.

Group: “S” you’ve got your “S”. You’ve got your “S”.

Leader: What does it spell?

Group: Jesus!

Leader: King of Kings

Group: Jesus!

Leader: Lord of Lords

Group: Jesus!

Leader: Mighty God

Group: Jesus!

*Mission Bible Class does not own the rights to this song.
